两把事。对于自己的私事都无法坦诚于自身，仅仅去找什么“意义”，什么“可能”，此等行径，与懦夫何异？<br><br>去正视自己！那是你的过去，现在，未来，与他人无关。你生活于你自身的历史之中，拥有的情感并非瞬时的经验。睁开双眼看清这捆缚你于此刻的东西，去迎接新的开始。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/38/33/383378.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1356800","time":"2018-6-19 16:53","userId":"keepchasing","userName":"KeepChasing","userSign":"(Watch More Anime!)","message":"说实话你这段文字我看不太懂。<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">难道你还在纠结于失恋的事情吗？</span><br>你可以想一想有没有其它你想要达成的目标，有多少算多少，让自己忙起来。<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">别告诉我除了恋爱你什么想法也没有。</span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1356809","time":"2018-6-19 17:28","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"","message":"确实还是和之前有关，一直想不通。现在知道都是因为想太多了，还是如你所说忙起来更好。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/84/208419.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1356801","time":"2018-6-19 16:54","userId":"bruse","userName":"土豆","userSign":"(✨️VIP 7✨️)","message":"费劲脑汁想搞明白帖子在说什么~  <br>“过去”的现在能够顾好~ 那么“过去”的“未来”的“现在”也不会是现在这样~<br>这不是在说后悔这件事嘛~<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/69.gif\" smileid=\"108\" alt=\"(bgm92)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211998.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1356804","time":"2018-6-19 17:06","userId":"211998","userName":"秘则为花","userSign":"","message":"费劲脑汁+1"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#8-2","id":"1356808","time":"2018-6-19 17:22","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"","message":"后悔与反省"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/44/14488.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1356810","time":"2018-6-19 17:29","userId":"sengohanabi","userName":"線香花火","userSign":"(Say A Little Prayer)","message":"LZ你在说什么（","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/35/23570.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1356814","time":"2018-6-19 17:36","userId":"htsune_miku","userName":"Jadeity","userSign":"","message":"就是我想太多了，不要瞎